===Verb===
{{en-verb|forgives|forgiving|forgave|forgiven}}

# {{lb|en|transitive}} To [[pardon]]; to [[waive]] any [[negative]] [[feeling]] or [[desire]] for [[punishment]], [[retribution]], or [[compensation]].
#: {{ux|en|Please '''forgive''' me if my phone goes off - I'm expecting an urgent call from my boss.}}
#: {{ux|en|'''Forgive''' others, not because they deserve forgiveness, but because you deserve peace.}}
#: {{ux|en|'''Forgive''' a debt, that is, tell a [[debtor]] that a repayment of a loan is no longer needed.}}
# {{lb|en|intransitive}} To [[accord]] [[forgiveness]].
